---
import { quickFacts } from '../config';
---

<section id="about" class="section animate-on-scroll">
  <header class="section__header">
    <span class="section__eyebrow">About</span>
    <h2 class="section__title">Quality is not an act, it's a habit.</h2>
  </header>

  <div class="about">
    <div class="about__body">
      <p>
        I'm a <strong>Senior SDET</strong> with 4.6 years of experience designing, developing, and implementing comprehensive
        <strong>test automation frameworks</strong> for web applications, APIs, and cloud-native architectures.
        Expert in using <em>AI-powered tools</em> (ChatGPT, Claude, Windsurf) to accelerate test case generation, optimize test scripts,
        and enhance debugging efficiency.
      </p>
      <p>
        Proficient in <strong>Playwright</strong>, <strong>Selenium</strong>, <strong>Postman</strong>, and <strong>K6</strong> for performance testing.
        Strong expertise in <em>CI/CD pipelines</em> (Jenkins, GitLab CI), <em>BDD</em> (Cucumber),
        <em>AWS services</em> (Lambda, S3, Cognito), and <em>database testing</em> (Oracle SQL, PostgreSQL).
      </p>
      <p>
        Demonstrated success in <strong>reducing regression cycles by 40%</strong>, improving test coverage by 35%, and mentoring junior engineers in automation best practices.
      </p>
    </div>
    <aside class="about__aside">
      <dl class="quick-facts">
        {quickFacts.map((f) => (
          <>
            <dt>{f.label}</dt>
            <dd>{f.value}</dd>
          </>
        ))}
      </dl>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>
